---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About the Treasury"
  titleZh="关于食养文库"
  description="About the Dragonfly Dharma 食养 Treasury — a bilingual educational resource on classical Chinese seasonal food wisdom."
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="page-hero" style="padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-hero__title-zh">关于食养文库</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__title-en">About the Treasury</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-2xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">

    <section class="article-section">
      <div class="article-section__label">
        <span class="article-section__label-zh">项目简介</span>
        <span class="article-section__label-en">About This Project</span>
      </div>
      <div class="article-section__content">
        <p>
          The <strong>Dragonfly Dharma 食养 Treasury</strong> is a bilingual educational resource
          dedicated to sharing classical Chinese wisdom on seasonal nourishment — 食养 (<em>shí yǎng</em>),
          the art of nourishing life through food aligned with the rhythms of nature and the seasons.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our content draws from foundational classical texts including the <em>Huangdi Neijing</em>
          (黄帝内经), the <em>Shennong Bencao Jing</em> (神农本草经), and other canonical works of
          Chinese medical and culinary literature. Each entry presents a verbatim classical passage,
          a bilingual reading, and a practical note for daily life.
        </p>
        <p>
          This project is an educational and cultural endeavour. It is not a medical resource, and
          nothing here constitutes medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="ornament-divider">· · ·</div>

    <section class="article-section">
      <div class="article-section__label">
        <span class="article-section__label-zh">关于本站</span>
        <span class="article-section__label-en">About This Site</span>
      </div>
      <div class="article-section__content">
        <p>
          关于本站：蜻蜓法门食养文库是一个双语教育资源，致力于分享中国传统节气食养智慧。
          内容取材自《黄帝内经》《神农本草经》等经典典籍，以教育与文化传播为目的。
        </p>
        <p>
          本站所有内容仅供教育与文化参考，不构成医疗建议、诊断或治疗建议。
          如有健康问题，请咨询持牌专业医疗人士。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="ornament-divider">· · ·</div>

    <section class="article-section">
      <div class="article-section__label">
        <span class="article-section__label-zh">内容框架</span>
        <span class="article-section__label-en">Content Framework</span>
      </div>
      <div class="article-section__content">
        <p>Each Treasury entry follows a consistent structure:</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-ink-muted); font-family: var(--font-sans); line-height: 1.8;">
          <li><strong>Classical Quote Block</strong> — a verbatim passage from the source text, in classical Chinese with source citation</li>
          <li><strong>English Reading</strong> — a contextual, educational reading of the passage</li>
          <li><strong>白话 Explanation</strong> — a plain-language Chinese explanation</li>
          <li><strong>In Practice / 在生活中</strong> — a short, practical note for daily life</li>
          <li><strong>Sources & Disclaimer</strong> — full citation and educational disclaimer</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Disclaimer box -->
    <div class="disclaimer" style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl);" role="note">
      <strong>Educational Disclaimer · 教育声明</strong>
      Educational &amp; cultural reference only — not medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.
      Consult a licensed practitioner. ·
      仅供教育与文化参考，非医疗建议、诊断或治疗，请咨询持牌专业人士。
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
